<br>
It may not be THE best one but the mage certainly rounds out the monk rather well.  A smart monk makes as good of a partner as just about anyone.<br>
<br>
The monk can:<br>
<br>
1) bring singles, which is very nice since a mage can solo nearly any single creature<br>
<br>
2) heal himself with mend and bandages<br>
<br>
3) provide that last bit of oomph that the mage needs to be efficient and let his pet do most of the work<br>
<br>
4) pull into the pet and take very little damage<br>
<br>
5) let the mage gate if there is trouble and then feign to save himself<br>
<br>
The mage can:<br>
<br>
1) provide heatstone/coldstone for the blind ass monk<br>
<br>
2) FREE bandages - this is humongous not just in money but hassle of carrying them and stopping to purchase them<br>
<br>
3) provide weightless bags so the monk can get some loot<br>
<br>
4) summon a 2hander to practice with so you dont have to carry one<br>
<br>
5) kill just about anything<br>
<br>
6) use their rains to maximum effect when 2 are pulled and the monk is on one and the pet is on the other <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uvilephire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vilephire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#333333>(5/31/01 4:11:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=192.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Shaman.</span><hr size=1> After 34+, the class I prefer to duo with most is a Shaman. Other classes have their advantages, but the Shaman is just the most well rounded, IMO. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ubalanzsonofanz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balanz son of Anz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 48<br> <font color=#333333>(5/31/01 3:45:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=192.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Blue Elf has been eating all the food lately!</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> That</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> was a heroic effort!</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
